comment: Adams (OKC) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Randolph's (MEM) drive.
Waiters (OKC) cleanly strips the ball from Lee (MEM).
Gasol (MEM) sets the screen on Waiters (OKC) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Westbrook (OKC) is in the paint for longer than 3 seconds without actively guarding a man.
Green (MEM) makes contact to Westbrook's (OKC) face with his knee on the layup attempt.
Singler (OKC) jumps vertically and legally contests Lee's (MEM) driving layup attempt.
Waiters (OKC) does not dislodge Conley (MEM) during rebounding.
Kanter (OKC) commits a take foul on Conley (MEM).
Morrow (OKC) commits a take foul on Green (MEM).
Westbrook (OKC) breaks the plane of the FT line before the ball makes contact with the rim.
Calathes (MEM) makes body to body contact with Westbrook (OKC) causing him to lose his balance and fall to the floor.
Adams (OKC) commits a take foul on Lee (MEM).
Adams (OKC) sets the screen on Udrih (MEM) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
